      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or budget-friendly option for someone handy. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few minor dents, and fading paint on the roof and hood. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will eventually need attention for a slow oil leak and some suspension wear that causes a bit of noise over bumps. The interior is mostly intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpet. It is a functional vehicle but expect to invest some time and effort into maintenance to bring it back to its best.",
